@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here
@roomId = paste-room-id-here
@inviteLinkToken = paste-invite-link-token-here

### 초대 링크 생성 (LEADER만 가능)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/project-rooms/{{roomId}}/invite-links
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expiresInHours": 72
}

### 초대 링크 정보 조회 (인증 불필요)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invite-links/{{inviteLinkToken}}

### 초대 링크 수락
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/invite-links/{{inviteLinkToken}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
